{"tid":1622281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院決定拒絕就禁蒙面法批出臨時禁制令","createTime":"2019-10-04T15:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T15:57:17.000Z","uid":121961,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef8472ddf9ebfa5dc2b00993047bfdff36e9658","tid":1622281,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484354-20191004.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484354-20191004.htm&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b0483473\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484354-20191004.htm&h=31f967ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484354-20191004.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n學聯前副袐書長岑敖暉及社民連梁國雄申請緊急臨時禁制令，要求禁止政府引用《緊急條例》訂立的《禁止蒙面規例》在午夜後生效，高等法院晚上開庭處理，決定拒絕批出臨時禁制令。"},{"pid":"b95b3c8762bc89598802f1898bcf442034efb9aa","tid":1622281,"uid":121961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:55:29.000Z","msg":"司法已死"},{"pid":"b1d9627fa9ec3ba2e3d7ca87f7cbf63fb9b51598","tid":1622281,"uid":25797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:55:53.000Z","msg":"香港法院由DQ議員同一地兩檢後已名存實亡"},{"pid":"8b57401fd041c3906a93e1ca66c9e089a6ca1aa5","tid":1622281,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"正式三權合作"},{"pid":"75b52c051e453eaa6584075e6c7ab33fa2db0a4b","tid":1622281,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:56:59.000Z","msg":"仲有法治？"},{"pid":"e86a904b61c8b0047e1308aa02e20be8bd6c2e1a","tid":1622281,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"特首真係大哂？"}]}